---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

import matchaIllustration from "../assets/Matcha.png"
import salon from "../assets/IMG_4586_result.webp"
import outside from "../assets/IMG_4543_result.webp"
import door from "../assets/IMG_4577_result.webp"
---
<Layout>
<h1>MENU</h1>
<div class="frametext_1">
<h2>BEHIND THE SCENES</h2>
<p>At Fred's, our menu is carefully curated based on what we enjoy the most when visiting a coffee bar.</p>
<p>We believe that good coffee is all about personality, so we've added our own creative twists to classic drinks - from signature matchas to flavorful lattes.</p>

<p>Whether you're in the mood for something sweet like a fresh pastry, or something savory to keep you going, we've got a little bit of everything.</p>
<p>It's all made with love - and with a focus on flavor, quality, and a cozy vibe you won't find anywhere else.</p>
</div>

<div class="collab_emmely">
<img src={matchaIllustration.src} alt="Matcha_illustration" />

<div class="frametext_2">
<h3>Available on June 1st!</h3>
<p>In collaboration with Emmely Moraitis, we've created a Pistachio Matcha - a fun and fresh new way to enjoy your matcha.</p>
<p>This unique blend brings together the earthy depth of matcha with the smooth, nutty flavor of pistachio - a combination we're pretty excited about!</p>
</div>
</div>

<div class="frametext_3">
<h2>ABOUT OUR MENU</h2>
<p>As a newly opened coffee bar, we handle all daily shopping ourselves.</p>
<p>Every morning, we head to Inco to buy what we need for the day. We aim to choose organic products whenever possible, and our chicken is halal.</p>
<p>At Fred's, it's important to us that everyone feels welcome!</p>
</div>
<div class="menu_3_img-container">
<img src={salon.src} alt="Salon" class="menu_3_img" />
<img src={outside.src} alt="Outside" class="menu_3_img" />
<img src={door.src} alt="Door" class="menu_3_img"/>
</div>

</Layout>
<style>
/* til mobilversion */
    /* billeder bliver sat til max-width 100% */
img {
  max-width: 100%;
}

h1{
  text-align: center;
 }

.frametext_1 h2, .frametext_3 h2{
  text-align: center;
}

.frametext_1, .frametext_2, .frametext_3{
border: 5px solid #FA719C;
  padding: 20px;
border-radius: 40px;
margin: 3rem auto;  /* placerer kasserne med text midt på siden*/
max-width: 380px;
}

.collab_emmely{
  background-color: #F7F1E6 ;
  padding: 20px 0; /* 20px top og bund, 0px til siderne */

}

.collab_emmely h3{
 color: #FA719C;
 text-align: center;
}
.menu_3_img {
  border-radius: 80px;
  width: 80%;             /* Gør billederne bredere */
  max-width: 300px;       /* Maksimal bredde for billederne */
  aspect-ratio: 1.5 / 2;  /* Mindre aflange billeder (højere end de er brede) */
  object-fit: cover;      /* Billedet fylder containeren uden at forvrænge */
  display: block;         /* Gør det muligt at centrere med margin */
  margin: 1rem auto;      /* Centrerer billederne vandret med luft omkring */
  margin-bottom: 40px;    /* Mere luft mellem billederne */
}




/* til computerversion */
@media screen and (min-width: 768px) {

  .collab_emmely {
    display: flex;         /* Bruger flexbox for at placere billede og tekst ved siden af hinanden */
    justify-content: space-between; /* Placerer elementerne med luft mellem dem */
    align-items: center;   /* Centrerer elementerne lodret */
    padding: 50px
}  
.collab_emmely img {
  width: 35%;
  margin-left: 100px;
}

.menu_3_img-container {
  display: flex;            /* Gør containeren til en flex container */
  justify-content: center;  /* Centrerer billederne horisontalt */
  width: 100%;              /* Containeren fylder hele bredden */
  margin: 0 auto;           /* Centrerer containeren på siden */
}    
  }

</style>